{"tid":1744334,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人權法過左 但有樣野仲未做","createTime":"2019-11-21T16:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T16:53:10.000Z","uid":111246,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc62097d301c551706cef7e8d3b466b77a2b21d2","tid":1744334,"uid":111246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"權法終於過左 但仲有樣野未做 就係去多謝d議員既幫手 冇佢地幫手 班官就唔會驚到瀨屎 無論佢地目的係咩 冇佢地幫手施壓 斷軍火 我地情況只會更壞 所以大家不如去多謝下佢地 希望係條法案之下 所有有份搞我地香港 搞我地市民既共產黨 共產黨既狗同班綠曱甴 都會受到制裁 而終有一日我地一定會贏同拎返所有我地失去既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">活著就要有尊嚴的活下去，像這樣像禽獸一樣永遠被關在籠子裏苟延殘喘的活著，我寧可選擇自由的死去</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Give me death or give me liberty</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HONGKONGLiberty/status/1197534888309743624?s=08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHONGKONGLiberty%2Fstatus%2F1197534888309743624%3Fs%3D08&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8zMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=08fd94c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHONGKONGLiberty%2Fstatus%2F1197534888309743624%3Fs%3D08&h=63d5b096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HONGKONGLiberty/status/1197534888309743624?s=08</a>"},{"pid":"3d98e1f7554d45eed1528c81708b490026a796b9","tid":1744334,"uid":111246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"557665f8797b148255949e56e2ad9c0fa1ecb394","tid":1744334,"uid":111246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e0b1fb8c4caf4389cdbf5bf1129e902e5aa3479e","tid":1744334,"uid":111246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":